air:Brand.Name: World Traveller
air:Brand.air:Title: World Traveller
WorldTvler
air:Brand.air:Text:
World Traveller is our full-service economy class on flights beyond Europe, packed with all the comfort and benefits you expect from British Airways at an affordable price. Your seat is ergonomically designed and comes with an adjustable headrest, lumbar support and recline.
• Great value all-inclusive fares with no hidden charges • Generous free baggage allowance • Delicious meals and full bar service • Personal entertainment system with complimentary headphones • Family-friendly features and kids' activity packs

air:Brand.Name: Economy Class
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Class
Economy
air:Brand.air:Text:
****Upgrade to Economy Comfort for extra space!****
Your Economy Class fare with KLM includes:
• Check in online. • Check in one bag max 23kg (additional baggage allowance applies for specific countries). • Carry on one bag + one other small item max combined weight 12kg. • Earn Flying Blue Miles. • Complimentary meals and drinks on board. • Rebooking or cancellation as per fare rules.
If the flight will be operated by another airline then the onboard product or service might be different.
Discover our high standards in Economy Class

air:Brand.Name: Economy Class
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Class
Economy
air:Brand.air:Text:
Your Lowest Available Fare ticket in Economy Class includes:
• Check in online. • Check in one bag max 23kg (additional baggage allowance applies for certain destinations). • Carry on one bag + one other small item max combined weight 12kg. • Earn Flying Blue Miles. • Complementary meals and drinks on board. • Rebooking or cancellation as per fare rules.
If the flight will be operated by another airline then the onboard product or service may differ.
Enjoy the comfort, quality and efficiency of Air France at attractive fares in the Economy cabi

air:Brand.Name: Economy Freedom
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Flex
EF
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Flex to benefit from the Priority Check in facility

The best inflight entertainment, selection of fine international cuisine, and warm Arabian hospitality. Welcome to Etihad’s Economy Class.
• Priority Check-in • 100% of Etihad Guest miles • Refer to fare rules for Refunds/Changes • Hand baggage x 1 bag at 7kgs • Upgrade eligibility • Neck pillows and soft fleece blankets • Tasty hot meals with a choice of three main courses, with vegetarian as standard • On board Cafe offering light snacks and a choice of teas, coffees and hot chocolate • Flying Nanny on board offering parents a helping hand on long-haul • Hundreds of hours of on-demand entertainment, on 10.6" screen with noise reduction headsets • Connectivity on board: Wi-Fi and mobile services • A range of connection ports at each seat, including USB and laptop power supply • Amenity kits with socks, eyeshades, earplugs, toothbrush and toothpaste on all long-haul and overnight flights. • Complimentary luxury coach services between Dubai / Al Ain and Abu Dhabi International Airport. • US Preclearance facility at Abu Dhabi Airport to pre clear US Immigration before guests board their flight to the US

air:Brand.Name: Economy Value
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Classic
EV
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Classic for a refund for a fee

The best inflight entertainment, selection of fine international cuisine, and warm Arabian hospitality. Welcome to Etihad Economy Class.
• 75% of Etihad Guest miles • Refer to fare rules for Refunds/Changes • Hand baggage x 1 bag at 7kgs • Upgrade eligibility • Neck pillows and soft fleece blankets • Tasty hot meals with a choice of three main courses, with vegetarian as standard • On board Cafe offering light snacks and a choice of teas, coffees and hot chocolate • Flying Nanny on board offering parents a helping hand on long-haul • Hundreds of hours of on-demand entertainment, on 10.6" screen with noise reduction headsets • Connectivity on board: Wi-Fi and mobile services • A range of connection ports at each seat, including USB and laptop power supply • Amenity kits with socks, eyeshades, earplugs, toothbrush and toothpaste on all long-haul and overnight flights. • Complimentary luxury coach services between Dubai / Al Ain and Abu Dhabi International Airport. • US Preclearance facility at Abu Dhabi Airport to pre clear US Immigration before guests board their flight to the US
